
What is LimaCharlie?

LimaCharlie is a cloud-based cybersecurity platform offering EDR (Endpoint Detection & Response), threat hunting, and security automation tools. It provides real-time telemetry, detection rules, and response capabilities via APIs. Key features include sensor-based endpoint monitoring, log ingestion, custom detections, and automated workflows.













